You&#39;re extending from `JPanel`, so when you do `add(cc)` in the `actionPerformed`, you&#39;re actually adding the component to the panel and not the frame.

Your problems are further compounded by the fact that `CarComponent` does not provide any kind sizing hints for the layout managers to work with.

Having said that, I would suggest making use of delegation workflow instead.  That is, create a concept of &quot;renderer&quot;, which can used by a &quot;render pane&quot; to draw the actual thing you want draw, then create different implementations of the &quot;renderer&quot;.

